Business Development
Specialists dedicated to sourcing investment opportunities and managing relationships.
Recent Activity:

PAEHQ: Arlington, VAIndustry: Aerospace, Defense & Government Services
Worldwide Flight ServicesHQ: Paris, FRIndustry: Transportation & Logistics
PrimeSourceHQ: Irving, TXIndustry: DistributionSeller: ITOCHU Corporation
Ying Shing EnterprisesHQ: Hong KongIndustry: Manufacturing
EnbiHQ: Shelbyville, INIndustry: ManufacturingSeller: Royal TenCate
MACtacHQ: Stow, OHIndustry: ManufacturingSeller: Bemis Company


The Platinum Equity business development team sources and reviews new investment opportunities.A Dedicated Team
The group, led by David Boutry in Los Angeles, is focused on originating new investment
opportunities and is composed of people who understand the needs of sellers. Organized
around key industries and geographies, our teams in Los Angeles, New York, London, and Singapore are practiced in identifying relevant and unique opportunities. The team
works alongside the M&A teams so Platinum Equity can concurrently develop
multiple investment opportunities.



















Focused on the Needs of Sellers
The Business Development team is driven to build and maintain
strong relationships with the corporate community, and with both global and
boutique investment banks. Understanding sellers’ needs allows Platinum Equity
to develop a differentiated approach and custom divestiture solutions.


