Platinum Equity, LLC Key Developments

Platinum Equity Promotes David Roberts as President and Chief Executive Officer
Jun 1 17
Platinum Equity announced it has completed the acquisition of American Traffic Solutions (ATS). In connection with the acquisition, David Roberts, previously ATS President and Chief Operating Officer has been promoted to President and Chief Executive Officer.


American Traffic Solutions Mulls Acquisitions
Jun 1 17
American Traffic Solutions, Inc. is looking for acquisition opportunities. Platinum Equity completed the acquisition of American Traffic Solutions. Platinum Equity, LLC Jacob Kotzubei said "We will bring Platinum Equity's financial, operational and M&A resources to bear in support of the company's long-term strategic plans," said Mr. Kotzubei. "ATS is a strong platform for growth, both organically and through prospective add-on acquisitions. We will pursue opportunities that can help broaden the company's service offering and expand its geographic reach."


Spotless Units Reportedly May Be Up For Grabs
Apr 27 17
Units of Spotless Group Holdings Limited (ASX:SPO) are reportedly up for grab. Spotless Group Holdings, which is advised by Citigroup Inc. (NYSE:C), has denied that any parts of the company are on the market, apart from a group of poorly performing contracts that it earlier indicated it would divest. Spotless Group Holdings had been in talks with a rival bidder, but those discussions were abandoned over the weekend. One possibility is that a party could be eager to buy Spotless Group Holdings without some of its smaller, less-successful components, and investment bankers are trying to find buyers for the unwanted divisions. Possible suitors could be smaller rival Delaware North, which has been approached before, or opportunistic private equity firms like Anchorage Capital Partners, Platinum Equity, LLC or Allegro.


